text.tspan: {{ trans("This is the Trade A Rate web app.", self) }}
{{ trans("But what does the app do?.", self) }}
{{ trans("Well are you an Android app developer?", self) }}
{{ trans("Sooo you want ratings for your app, right?", self) }}
{{ trans("You could pay for your ratings!", self) }}
{{ trans("Or ... you trade ratings with other app developers!", self) }}
{{ trans("So what do you need to do for a review?", self) }}
{{ trans("Add your trade with the 'Add' button on the bottom of the 'All trades' page!", self) }}
{{ trans("Fill in your app id in the input field and click submit.", self) }}
{{ trans("When an other developer joins your trade, you will get an email.", self) }}
{{ trans("With the news that someone has joined your trade and a link to the trade.", self) }}
{{ trans("If conditions of the trade seem reasonable to you.", self) }}
{{ trans("You can click 'Accept' on the bottom of the trade.", self) }}
{{ trans("If the other developer also accepted the trade the trade status will change to accepted and both developer's can start to review.", self) }}
{{ trans("(You can also see that your starter trade points will allow you to have only one outstanding trade !)", self) }}
{{ trans("Be sure to review the app of the other developer in", self) }}
{{ trans("the same browser", self) }}
{{ trans("that you use for Trade A Rate since the localization is important!", self) }}
{{ trans("dont forget that you have to install the other developer's app", self) }}
{{ trans("If both developer's did the reviews of each others app the Trade A Rate system will detect those reviews in a maximum of nine hours.", self) }}
{{ trans("Both partys will be awarded a review point, when you collect 10 point you can do 2 reviews at the same time.", self) }}
{{ trans("when you collect 20 points you can do 3 reviews. (you get 20 bonus points for now, so you can be involved with 3 trades at a time)", self) }}
{{ trans("Most important part you have earned a trade point and got a organic review!", self) }}
{{ trans("Or join a trade that someone else started by going to a trade detail (with status initiated).", self) }}
{{ trans("And join that trade on the bottom of the trade detail page.", self) }}
{{ trans("Fill in your app id in the input field and click submit.", self) }}
{{ trans("You will now get an email that you joined someones trade.", self) }}
{{ trans("In this email you will find a link to the trade you are in.", self) }}
